description: If you’re drivin’ through “The D” and you see Frackin’ Hungry on the streets, you must stop and meet Chefs Chris & Jess, and order up a dish of their gourmet-on-the-go cuisine, because it’s indeed the best. At this delightfully designed truck, you’ll find quite a few highly delicious “truck-made” items, including Corned Beef Stacks (with grilled potato bread, braised cabbage, and gooey cheese sauce), Confit Yukon Gold Potatoes (the perfect mix of creamy and crispy with fresh herbs and cheese),  Veggie Burgers (with tomato pepper jam, avocado smash, and fresh greens), and more. The next time you’re feeling famished, quit snackin’ and head straight to Frackin’ Hungry.
name: Frackin' Hungry
